{"tid":1548420,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[多圖] 狗女: 放火就係得到民主嘅方法？","createTime":"2019-09-07T04:13:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T06:29:32.000Z","uid":58888,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c081ca23674f0f845c0365dfb7e6fb465875ca34","tid":1548420,"uid":58888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:13:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n有嗰frd間中學多狗仔女讀 <br />\n咁啱見到有個夠二代有新story<br />\n諗緊佢係咪終於出聲清算屋企嘅黑警<br />\n原來佢問緊放火係咪取得民主嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QRZQWjb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQRZQWjb.png&h=94c69553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇hk01 知咩事啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0W3RFNz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0W3RFNz.png&h=0c0d6b60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n條狗女冇記錯屋企人當差<br />\nfc住<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>荔景紀律部隊宿舍</strong></span><br />\n攞納稅人錢津貼式去英國讀書<br />\n嚟緊2019-2020 讀 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>CARDIFF UNIVERSITY</strong></span><br />\n去英國之前讀<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>基督教崇真中學</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W3MWRUf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW3MWRUf.png&h=bcbfd9b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢老母 要屌就認住啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e40pgkY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe40pgkY.png&h=aaf25651&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左：屋企隻真狗 右：唔sure係咪老豆 都似嘅都<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/07/005414_fbf929808c168e23328af0270304b7fc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F07%2F005414_fbf929808c168e23328af0270304b7fc.png&h=844801dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屋企隻真狗<br />\n<br />\n唔sure係老豆定老母係黑警 <br />\n唔夠料上報老豆搵仔<br />\n歡迎fc提供資料<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>禍必及妻兒<br />\n全部都要清算</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n721 811 831<br />\n</strong></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0ZETsi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0ZETsi.jpg&h=adb9555b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQSyXTZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQSyXTZ.jpg&h=fe0f2d9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z7hK4yZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz7hK4yZ.jpg&h=35250aee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1jPBbd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1jPBbd0.jpg&h=b4c400d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x4R4j7k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx4R4j7k.jpg&h=02afe750&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57030c4b0a03557c7c6c319faa7c1740e61a6f73","tid":1548420,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:14:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 終極文宣 對準政權 全民抗共</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fd3cdb1a5cd259b94e89096acde424b145af6e4","tid":1548420,"uid":58888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:15:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bde42b7c7542